"title": "1125: God, righteousness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1125: god, righteousness of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An aspect of God's nature which expresses his unique moral perfection and his readiness to save sinners. It is made known especially through the gospel of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>God's nature is righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:137\">PSA 119:137</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:10\">PSA 48:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:2\">PSA 97:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:142\">PSA 119:142</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:17\">PSA 145:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:21\">ISA 45:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:1\">JER 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:25\">JHN 17:25</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness shows his sovereignty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:19\">PSA 71:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:23\">JOB 37:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:6\">PSA 36:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:6\">PSA 97:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:16\">ISA 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness is eternal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:3\">PSA 111:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:3\">PSA 112:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:9\">PSA 112:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:142\">PSA 119:142</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:160\">PSA 119:160</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:8\">ISA 51:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's actions are righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:14\">DAN 9:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:11\">JDG 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:7\">1SA 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">REV 15:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's rule is righteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:8\">PSA 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:3-2Sam23:4\">2SA 23:3–23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:13\">PSA 96:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:4\">PSA 99:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteous acts are saving acts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:5\">PSA 65:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:10\">PSA 40:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:4-Ps116:6\">PSA 116:4–116:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps129:4\">PSA 129:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:13\">ISA 46:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:16\">DAN 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:5\">MIC 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness vindicates his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:24\">PSA 35:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:2-Ps4:3\">PSA 4:2–4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:9\">PSA 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:4\">PSA 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:6\">PSA 103:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:8\">ISA 50:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:9\">MIC 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33\">ROM 8:33</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness shows his faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:8\">NEH 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:1\">PSA 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:5\">ZEP 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:8\">ZEC 8:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness shows his justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:20\">JER 11:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:3\">JOB 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:7\">PSA 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:6\">PSA 50:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:4\">PSA 51:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:12\">PRO 21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:17\">ECC 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness is seen in his judgments</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:11\">PSA 7:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:5-2Chr12:6\">2CH 12:5–12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:15\">EZR 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:22\">ISA 10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:17\">ISA 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:18\">LAM 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:2\">ROM 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's laws show his righteousness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:8-Ps19:9\">PSA 19:8–19:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:8\">DEU 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:4\">PSA 33:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:7\">PSA 119:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:144\">PSA 119:144</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:32\">ROM 1:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:12\">ROM 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:4\">ROM 8:4</a></p>\n<h2>God's righteousness contrasts with human unrighteousness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:5\">ROM 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:27\">EXO 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:33\">NEH 9:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:17\">JOB 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:2\">JOB 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:7\">DAN 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:3\">ROM 10:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's righteousness is revealed primarily in Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21-Rom3:22\">ROM 3:21–3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:2–11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:6\">JER 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:14\">ACT 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:4\">ROM 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:30\">1CO 1:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:1\">2PE 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1\">1JN 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness is revealed in the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:9\">PHP 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>God gives his righteousness to believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:22-Rom4:24\">ROM 4:22–4:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:6\">GEN 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:26\">JOB 33:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:12\">HOS 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:22\">ROM 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:3-Rom4:8\">ROM 4:3–4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:17\">ROM 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:4\">ROM 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit reveals God's righteousness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:5\">GAL 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">JHN 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:10\">JHN 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17\">ROM 14:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's righteousness is to be sought after</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:1\">ISA 51:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:3\">ZEP 2:3</a></p>\n<h2>God's righteousness is a pattern for human living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:7\">1JN 3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:19\">GEN 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">HOS 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">EPH 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:29\">1JN 2:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:12\">1JN 3:12</a></p>\n<h2>God's righteousness is worthy of praise</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:15-Isa24:16\">ISA 24:15–24:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:17\">PSA 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:31\">PSA 22:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:28\">PSA 35:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:14\">PSA 51:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:15\">PSA 71:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:24\">PSA 71:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:7\">PSA 145:7</a></p>",
